    "abstractNote": "The article is devoted to Letter to Publius, which has not been previously translated into Russian. This Letter belongs to the pen of the Syrian writer and saint of 4 century Ephrem the Syrian (Mar Aphrem of Nisibis) (c. 306\u2013373). The \u00abLetter to Publius\u00bb is a reflection on the subject of the Last Judgment, which awaits every person \u2014 a reflection that is replete with numerous images that are very often found in other genuine writings of St. Ephrem.",
